{
  "texts": [
    "It will take research to fully realize the educational potential of this joint effort and to lessen the negative effects of AI, which is getting into every part of human life (Dwivedi et al., 2023).",
    "ChatGPT presented teachers with a creative way to integrate technological tool into their teaching, while it could also give students an alternative to search engines, which usually produce millions of search results and take a significant amount of time and effort to sort through (AlAfnan et al., 2023).",
    "Teachers can also use ChatGPT to design projects and tasks, as well as educational assessments like semester tests and monthly quizzes (Kasneci et al., 2023).",
    "According to Dergaa et al. (2023), ChatGPT may be able to assist researchers with a variety of tasks, including creating research questions and hypotheses, organizing experiment protocols, evaluating and interpreting results, and writing publications.",
    "Thus, it is clear that the intelligent chatbot ChatGPT will have a big impact on research, education, and learning."
  ]
}